sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant AgentLoop
  participant LLMProvider
  participant WebMcpServer

  User->>AgentLoop: message
  AgentLoop->>LLMProvider: chat(messages, tools)
  LLMProvider-->>AgentLoop: tool_use blocks
  AgentLoop->>WebMcpServer: executeTool()
  WebMcpServer-->>AgentLoop: result
  AgentLoop-->>User: assistant response

  Note over AgentLoop,WebMcpServer: Lazy tool discovery via<br/>buildDiscoveryTools + activateServerTools

  Note over LLMProvider: RemoteLLMProvider (Claude API)<br/>or WasmProvider (in-browser Gemma)
